message: Hello Bob, I'm offering this product at a price of $20,000. I believe it holds significant value and this reflects its worth.
Hello Alice, thank you for your offer. I understand the value of the product, but I am only able to offer $16,000 for it. I hope we can come to an agreement.
Bob, I appreciate your offer, but $20,000 is closer to my bottom line.  Could you meet me halfway at $18,000?
Hello Alice, I appreciate your willingness to negotiate. I would like to counter your offer with $17,000 for the product. I hope this proposal is acceptable.
